In [28]:
##### filtering step
# mean sample_GQ >= 30
# sample r_het_hom_vars in [1,2]
# sample r_ti_tv > 2
# sample r_insertion_deletion in [0.5, 1.2]

#geno.filter_cols(geno.sample_qc.dp_stats.mean >= 4)

geno_f = geno.filter_cols(geno.sample_qc.r_het_hom_var > 1)
geno_f = geno_f.filter_cols(geno_f.sample_qc.r_het_hom_var < 2)
geno_f = geno_f.filter_cols(geno_f.sample_qc.r_ti_tv >2)
geno_f = geno_f.filter_cols(geno_f.sample_qc.r_insertion_deletion >0.5)
geno_f = geno_f.filter_cols(geno_f.sample_qc.r_insertion_deletion <1.2)

geno_f = geno_f.filter_cols(geno_f.sample_qc.gq_stats.mean >= 30)

#### Kinship analysis
